info.author: Paul Wouters, based on work by Francis Markham
info.description:
This module allows you to obtain geo information about your current location.
It uses NetworkManager to obtain a list of wifi networks, and queries the
Google location service for information. A module and a commandline tool is
available.
info.name: geome
info.summary: Locate yourself based on wifi signals and IP address
